            h4 What programming languages are available?
            p We currently support Python and JavaScript.
            p
              b Why should you choose Python? 
              span Python is both beginner-friendly and currently used by major corporations (such as Google). If you have younger or first-time learners, we strongly recommend Python.
            p
              b Why should you choose JavaScript? 
              span JavaScript is the language of the web and is used across nearly every website. You may prefer to choose JavaScript if you are planning to also study web development. Weâ€™ve also made it easy for students to transition from Python to JavaScript-based web development.
            p JavaScriptâ€™s syntax is a little more difficult for beginners than Python, so if you cannot decide between the two, we recommend Python.
